---
title: Seared Salmon & Herb-Butter Sauce with Steamed Veggies & Mashed Potato
description: Classic ingredients don’t need much to elevate them to a sensational meal. Take this delicious salmon—it just gets
simply seared then topped with a herb-infused butter for a meal that’s low on effort and high on taste.

